file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  description: This API descripes the online evaluation service, as accessed by the
    user and organizers.
  title: Evaluation
  version: "1.0"
servers:
- url: https://eval.mathphys.info/v1
paths:
  /faculties:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Faculty'
                type: array
          description: OK
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Faculty'
        description: Changes possible to a faculty
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Faculty'
          description: OK
  /faculties/{facultyId}:
    get:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the faculty to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: facultyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Faculty'
          description: OK
      summary: Get a faculty by ID
    patch:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the faculty to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: facultyId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Faculty'
        description: Changes possible to a faculty
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":

            application/json:

                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Faculty'
          description: OK
      summary: Change a faculty by ID

        required: true
      responses:

            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Term'
          description: OK
  /terms/{termId}:

      parameters:
      - description: ID of the term to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: termId
        required: true
        schema:

      responses:

            application/json:

                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Term'
          description: OK
      summary: Get a term by ID
    patch:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the term to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: termId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Term'
        description: Changes possible to a term
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Term'
          description: OK
      summary: Change a term by ID
  /terms/{termId}/report:
    get:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the term to get report from
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: termId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/TermReport'
          description: OK
      summary: Get a term report
  /modules:

      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Module'
                type: array
          description: OK
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:

        description: Changes possible to a module

        "200":

  /modules/{moduleId}:

        explode: false
        in: path
        name: moduleId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:

      summary: Deletes a module by ID
    get:
      parameters:

        explode: false

        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:

    patch:
      parameters:

        style: simple

      summary: Deletes a module by ID
    get:
      parameters:

        explode: false

        name: courseId
        required: true

      summary: Get a course by ID
    patch:

        name: courseId
        required: true

      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Course'
        description: Changes possible to a course
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Course'
          description: OK
      summary: Change a course by ID
  /courses/{courseId}/report:
    get:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the course to generate report
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: courseId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":

  /profs:

    post:

        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:

          description: OK
  /profs/{profId}:
    delete:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the prof to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: profId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "204":
          description: OK
      summary: Deletes a module by ID
    get:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the prof to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: profId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Prof'
          description: OK
      summary: Get a prof by ID
    patch:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the prof to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: profId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:

        description: Changes possible to a prof
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Prof'
          description: OK
      summary: Change a prof by ID
  /courseprofs:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/CourseProf'
                type: array
          description: OK
    post:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/CourseProf'
        description: Changes possible to a courseprof
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CourseProf'
          description: OK
  /courseprofs/{courseProfId}:
    delete:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the courseprof to get
        explode: false

    get:

    patch:

  /courses/{courseId}/tutors:

      requestBody:

        description: Changes possible to a tutor
        required: true
      responses:

              schema:

          description: OK
  /courses/{courseId}/tutors/{tutorId}:

      parameters:

        explode: false
        in: path
        name: courseId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: ID of the tutor to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: tutorId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "204":
          description: OK
      summary: Deletes a tutor by ID
    get:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the course
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: courseId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: ID of the tutor to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: tutorId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tutor'
          description: OK
      summary: Get a tutor by ID
    patch:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the course
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: courseId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: ID of the tutor to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: tutorId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tutor'
        description: Changes possible to a tutor
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tutor'
          description: OK
      summary: Change a tutor by ID
  /courses/{courseId}/tutors/{tutorId}/report:
    get:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the course, in which the tutor lives to generate report
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: courseId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: ID of the tutor to generate report
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: tutorId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:

          content:
            application/json:
              schema:

  /questionaire/{invitationId}:

        explode: false

        required: true
        schema:

        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":

            application/json:
              schema:

          description: OK

      - description: ID of the invitation
        explode: false
        in: path

        required: true

        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Questionaire'

        required: true

            schema:

        description: Changes possible to a form
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Form'
          description: OK
  /forms/{formId}:
    get:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the form to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: formId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Form'
          description: OK

    patch:
      parameters:
      - description: ID of the form to get
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: formId
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Form'
        description: Changes possible to a form
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Form'
          description: OK

components:
  schemas:
    Faculty:
      example:
        name: name
        id: id
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
      required:
      - name
      type: object
    Term:
      example:
        name: name
        end: 2000-01-23
        id: id
        begin: 2000-01-23
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        begin:
          format: date
          type: string
        end:
          format: date
          type: string
      required:
      - begin
      - end
      - name
      type: object
    Module:
      description: used to keep track of courses over many years.
      example:
        facultyId: facultyId
        name: name
        description: description
        id: id
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        description:
          type: string
        facultyId:
          description: Determines which faculty is in charge.
          type: string
      required:
      - description
      - facultyId
      - name
      type: object
    Course:
      example:
        formId: formId
        termId: termId
        thirdPartyKey: thirdPartyKey
        tutors:
        - thirdPartyKey: thirdPartyKey
          name: name
          censoredDate: 2000-01-23
          id: id
          censored: true
          email: email
        - thirdPartyKey: thirdPartyKey
          name: name
          censoredDate: 2000-01-23
          id: id
          censored: true
          email: email
        progress: created
        clearance: clearance
        location: location
        language: language
        id: id
        moduleId: moduleId
        numberOfStudents: 0
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        moduleId:
          type: string
        formId:
          type: string
        termId:
          type: string
        location:
          type: string
        numberOfStudents:
          type: integer
        language:
          type: string
        thirdPartyKey:
          description: Third-party Key, that identifies a course
          type: string
        progress:
          description: current status for sent mails for this course
          enum:
          - created
          - announced
          - inEval
          - processing
          - published
          type: string
        clearance:
          description: Describes whether, this course is published to profs and tutors.
          type: string
        tutors:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Tutor'
          type: array
      required:
      - clearance
      - formId
      - language
      - location
      - moduleId
      - numberOfStudents
      - progress
      - termId
      - tutors
      type: object
    Prof:
      example:
        firstname: firstname
        censoredDate: 2000-01-23
        id: id
        title: title
        censored: true
        email: email
        lastname: lastname
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        firstname:
          type: string
        lastname:
          type: string
        title:
          type: string
        censored:
          description: Determines, whether public reports can include, this persons
            results.
          type: boolean
        censoredDate:
          description: Date of agreement that results can be published
          format: date
          type: string
        email:
          description: Used to communicate to prof.
          format: email
          type: string
      required:
      - censored
      - censoredDate
      - email
      - firstname
      - lastname
      - title
      type: object
    CourseProf:
      description: creates a link between courses and prof
      example:
        id: id
        courseId: courseId
        profId: profId
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        courseId:
          type: string
        profId:
          type: string
      required:
      - courseId
      - profId
      type: object
    Tutor:
      description: Subteacher, only sees portions of the results of his course. Currently
        they are created for every year newly.
      example:
        thirdPartyKey: thirdPartyKey
        name: name
        censoredDate: 2000-01-23
        id: id
        censored: true
        email: email
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
        censored:
          description: Determines, whether public reports can include, this persons
            results.
          type: boolean
        censoredDate:
          description: Date of agreement that results can be published
          format: date
          type: string
        thirdPartyKey:
          description: Third-party Key, that identifies a tutor.
          type: string
        email:
          format: email
          type: string
      required:
      - censored
      - censoredDate
      - email
      - name
      type: object
    Invitation:
      description: Onetime invitation to take a certain evaluation of a course.
      example:
        id: id
        used: true
        courseId: courseId
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        courseId:
          type: string
        validBegin:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        validEnd:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        used:
          type: boolean
      required:
      - courseId
      type: object
    EmptyForm:
      description: Empty Form to be completed by student.
      example:
        tutors:
        - thirdPartyKey: thirdPartyKey
          name: name
          censoredDate: 2000-01-23
          id: id
          censored: true
          email: email
        - thirdPartyKey: thirdPartyKey
          name: name
          censoredDate: 2000-01-23
          id: id
          censored: true
          email: email
        abstractForm:
          pages:
          - id: id
            sections:
            - questions:
              - isMulti: false
                isComment: true
                hasNotApplicableOption: true
                options:
                - id: id
                  label:
                    key: label
                  value: 0
                - id: id
                  label:
                    key: label
                  value: 0
                id: id
                hasOtherOption: true
                visualizer: histogram
                shortcode: shortcode
                title:
                  key: title
                regards: course
              - isMulti: false
                isComment: true
                hasNotApplicableOption: true
                options:
                - id: id
                  label:
                    key: label
                  value: 0
                - id: id
                  label:
                    key: label
                  value: 0
                id: id
                hasOtherOption: true
                visualizer: histogram
                shortcode: shortcode
                title:
                  key: title
                regards: course
              id: id
              title:
                key: title
            - questions:
              - isMulti: false
                isComment: true
                hasNotApplicableOption: true
                options:
                - id: id
                  label:
                    key: label
                  value: 0
                - id: id
                  label:
                    key: label
                  value: 0
                id: id
                hasOtherOption: true
                visualizer: histogram
                shortcode: shortcode
                title:
                  key: title
                regards: course
              - isMulti: false
                isComment: true
                hasNotApplicableOption: true
                options:
                - id: id
                  label:
                    key: label
                  value: 0
                - id: id
                  label:
                    key: label
                  value: 0
                id: id
                hasOtherOption: true
                visualizer: histogram
                shortcode: shortcode
                title:
                  key: title
                regards: course
              id: id
              title:
                key: title
          - id: id
            sections:
            - questions:
              - isMulti: false
                isComment: true
                hasNotApplicableOption: true
                options:
                - id: id
